SimulationType                   Numerical
#SimulationType                   Minimization
SimulationType                   MC
NumberOfCycles                   200
NumberOfInitializationCycles     10
NumberOfEquilibrationCycles      0
PrintEvery                       100
RestartFile                      no

#RandomSeed 1361016699

RMSGradientTolerance 1e-6
MaxGradientTolerance 1e-6
MaximumStepLength 0.1

Ensemble NVT

CutOff                           12.0
ChargeChargeCutOff               10.0
ChargeMethod                     Ewald
Forcefield                       Local
EwaldPrecision                   1e-8
TimeStep                         0.00005

#OmitEwaldFourier yes

Framework 0
Frameworkname CHA_SI
RemoveAtomNumberCodeFromLabel yes
UnitCells 1 1 1
ReplicaUnitCells 3 3 3
RestrictFrameworkAtomsToBox yes
ExternalPressure 1.0e7
ExternalTemperature 800.0
PutMoleculeOnBarrier             yes
BarrierPosition                  0.5 0.5 0.0
Movies yes
WriteMoviesEvery 1
FlexibleFramework no

#FixedAdsorbateGroupOrientationZ 0 0

CFLambdaMoveProbability 0.0

